content: Hello! Thank you for reaching out to XYZ Home Services. How can I assist you today? We provide plumbing, electrical, and HVAC services.

I understand, it looks like this may be a misdial. If you need any home service help in the future, feel free to contact us. Otherwise, have a great day! I'll close this chat now.
